1935
00:56:08,240 --> 00:56:09,060
(What other secrets
is Manager Tui hiding?)

1936
00:56:20,260 --> 00:56:22,020
(Group Interrogation:
10-minute time limit)

1937
00:56:22,060 --> 00:56:22,940
(Group Interrogation)

1938
00:56:22,940 --> 00:56:24,040
(Goal: Detectives initiate a trial)

1939
00:56:24,040 --> 00:56:25,460
(Conduct a 10-minute interrogation
on a specific suspect or NPC)

1940
00:56:25,470 --> 00:56:26,980
(to advance the investigation.)

1941
00:56:27,680 --> 00:56:29,520
Alright, fellow detectives.

1942
00:56:29,520 --> 00:56:30,440
Time to get to work.

1943
00:56:30,440 --> 00:56:32,160
(Hitting her right in the feels)
I love it when you call us that.

1944
00:56:32,300 --> 00:56:33,500
(Smooth talker)

1945
00:56:33,840 --> 00:56:34,760
Come on.

1946
00:56:34,760 --> 00:56:35,720
Since we can

1947
00:56:35,720 --> 00:56:37,240
narrow it down to five suspects,

1948
00:56:37,240 --> 00:56:37,640
right?

1949
00:56:37,640 --> 00:56:38,480
(Suspect list: Ning Bubble, He Yiwei,)
So,

1950
00:56:38,480 --> 00:56:39,280
(Ke Coffee, Qian Jinding,)
should we

1951
00:56:39,280 --> 00:56:40,080
(Liu Lian Wangfan)
bring up...

1952
00:56:40,080 --> 00:56:41,440
Bring up the other

1953
00:56:41,440 --> 00:56:42,200
likely suspect.

1954
00:56:42,880 --> 00:56:44,640
Let's call him out.

1955
00:56:44,640 --> 00:56:46,240
Time for you, Liu Lian Wangfan,

1956
00:56:46,240 --> 00:56:47,560
the culprit, to take the stand.

1957
00:56:48,000 --> 00:56:49,240
Liu Lian Wangfan.

1958
00:56:49,360 --> 00:56:50,440
Still smirking?

1959
00:56:50,440 --> 00:56:51,120
Sit down.

1960
00:56:51,120 --> 00:56:51,920
Take a seat.

1961
00:56:52,640 --> 00:56:53,800
We meet again.

1962
00:56:53,800 --> 00:56:54,920
Here's the deal today.

1963
00:56:54,920 --> 00:56:56,760
A really serious crime just happened.

1964
00:56:57,360 --> 00:56:58,360
What crime?

1965
00:56:58,360 --> 00:56:59,920
Manager Tui is dead.

1966
00:57:03,080 --> 00:57:04,080
How could he be dead?

1967
00:57:04,840 --> 00:57:05,480
You didn't know?

1968
00:57:05,480 --> 00:57:06,400
What are you playing dumb for?

1969
00:57:06,400 --> 00:57:07,400
Didn't you go see him

1970
00:57:07,400 --> 00:57:08,240
with a hammer?

1971
00:57:09,080 --> 00:57:09,920
You were caught on camera.

1972
00:57:09,920 --> 00:57:10,420
(Bluffing)

1973
00:57:10,840 --> 00:57:11,600
Caught on camera?

1974
00:57:18,240 --> 00:57:19,840
His right pocket.

1975
00:57:21,220 --> 00:57:22,540
(Staring intently)

1976
00:57:22,560 --> 00:57:23,680
We need to do

1977
00:57:23,680 --> 00:57:25,080
a body search right now.

1978
00:57:25,080 --> 00:57:26,120
If you're innocent,

1979
00:57:26,120 --> 00:57:27,640
you shouldn't be afraid
of us searching you.

1980
00:57:27,840 --> 00:57:29,120
Go ahead, search me all you want.

1981
00:57:29,760 --> 00:57:30,600
There's nothing on me.

1982
00:57:34,720 --> 00:57:35,800
I'm clean.

1983
00:57:37,760 --> 00:57:39,640
I don't think you're that clean.

1984
00:57:40,840 --> 00:57:41,520
What's this?

1985
00:57:43,480 --> 00:57:43,880
Medicine.

1986
00:57:44,320 --> 00:57:45,040
Medicine?

1987
00:57:45,720 --> 00:57:46,360
ClearSight.

1988
00:57:46,360 --> 00:57:47,300
(Evidence found:
ClearSight medicine bottle)

1989
00:57:47,440 --> 00:57:49,960
The world is full
of flashing lights that blind you.

1990
00:57:49,960 --> 00:57:52,720
But you have a clear sight.

1991
00:57:55,400 --> 00:57:56,040
And a phone.

1992
00:57:56,100 --> 00:57:57,420
(Evidence found:
Liu Lian Wangfan's phone)

1993
00:57:57,560 --> 00:57:58,560
His lower back.

1994
00:57:59,560 --> 00:58:00,280
Is there a...

1995
00:58:00,800 --> 00:58:01,360
hammer?

1996
00:58:01,840 --> 00:58:03,320
There's nothing on his lower back.

1997
00:58:03,320 --> 00:58:04,780
(Completely empty)

1998
00:58:05,780 --> 00:58:07,860
(Detective springing into action)

1999
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:08,600
There's really nothing.

2000
00:58:08,600 --> 00:58:09,440
See?

2001
00:58:09,440 --> 00:58:10,360
Anything? Nope.

2002
00:58:10,360 --> 00:58:11,360
Alright, I believe you.

2003
00:58:11,360 --> 00:58:12,580
(I don't believe you)

2004
00:58:15,040 --> 00:58:15,960
There's really nothing.

2005
00:58:16,560 --> 00:58:17,440
Wait a minute.

2006
00:58:18,740 --> 00:58:20,180
(Evidence found: Mysterious paper)

2007
00:58:20,880 --> 00:58:21,600
I believe you.

2008
00:58:22,240 --> 00:58:23,040
There's really nothing on me.

2009
00:58:25,900 --> 00:58:27,220
(Evidence found: Blood-stained gauze)

2010
00:58:27,300 --> 00:58:28,240
(Can only smile and play dumb)

2011
00:58:28,240 --> 00:58:28,720
Are you serious?

2012
00:58:28,720 --> 00:58:29,040
Nice search.

2013
00:58:30,300 --> 00:58:31,040
(Be proactive)
Suspect.

2014
00:58:31,640 --> 00:58:32,200
Here.

2015
00:58:32,200 --> 00:58:33,420
(Deeply respectful)

2016
00:58:35,240 --> 00:58:36,800
Come on, hurry up.

2017
00:58:36,800 --> 00:58:37,480
Okay.

2018
00:58:37,480 --> 00:58:39,040
Ask him about the gauze first.

2019
00:58:39,040 --> 00:58:40,680
What shape is on the gauze?

2020
00:58:42,480 --> 00:58:42,960
Hearts.

2021
00:58:42,960 --> 00:58:43,700
(Heart-shaped bloodstain)

2022
00:58:43,840 --> 00:58:44,760
Who has the heart?

2023
00:58:45,520 --> 00:58:46,240
It's him.

2024
00:58:46,240 --> 00:58:46,680
Yes.

2025
00:58:46,780 --> 00:58:48,140
(Heart-shaped hammer: Ning Bubble)
The heart.

2026
00:58:48,160 --> 00:58:49,640
So it's confirmed that the person I hit

2027
00:58:49,640 --> 00:58:50,520
was him.

2028
00:58:50,520 --> 00:58:51,860
(Ning Bubble attacked Liu Lian Wangfan)

2029
00:58:52,320 --> 00:58:54,000
Where did this
heart-shaped wound come from?

2030
00:58:54,000 --> 00:58:55,040
I was

2031
00:58:55,040 --> 00:58:56,360
hit by someone with a hammer.

2032
00:58:56,360 --> 00:58:57,080
I used that to wrap the wound.

2033
00:58:57,080 --> 00:58:58,180
(Confirmed being hit by a hammer)

2034
00:58:58,320 --> 00:58:59,680
There's a text message here

2035
00:58:59,680 --> 00:59:00,680
sent by your lackey.

2036
00:59:00,680 --> 00:59:01,400
Liu, I'm so sorry.

2037
00:59:01,400 --> 00:59:03,040
I accidentally
burned a hole in the clothes

2038
00:59:03,040 --> 00:59:04,320
you asked me to iron.

2039
00:59:04,320 --> 00:59:06,880
Did you steal Ding's

2040
00:59:06,880 --> 00:59:07,760
puppet costume

2041
00:59:07,760 --> 00:59:09,920
and changed into it here?

2042
00:59:09,920 --> 00:59:11,900
(Liu Lian Wangfan stole
Ding Pudding's puppet costume?)

2043
00:59:14,420 --> 00:59:15,900
(Silence)

2044
00:59:16,720 --> 00:59:17,520
Silence, huh?

2045
00:59:17,520 --> 00:59:18,440
Alright, let's keep searching.

2046
00:59:18,440 --> 00:59:20,840
There's a note here saying,
"Protecting My Privacy".

2047
00:59:20,840 --> 00:59:21,660
(Protecting My Privacy)

2048
00:59:22,560 --> 00:59:23,560
Not only will I

2049
00:59:23,560 --> 00:59:25,200
teach you how to protect yourself,

2050
00:59:25,200 --> 00:59:26,800
but I will also protect you

2051
00:59:26,800 --> 00:59:28,320
and help you get rid
of anyone who hurts you.

2052
00:59:29,800 --> 00:59:30,360
Okay.

2053
00:59:30,360 --> 00:59:31,160
Let's hear it,

2054
00:59:31,160 --> 00:59:32,120
What's this about?

2055
00:59:32,840 --> 00:59:33,960
I wrote that line.

2056
00:59:36,920 --> 00:59:37,600
Because

2057
00:59:37,600 --> 00:59:39,200
I wanted to get revenge for my sister.

2058
00:59:42,760 --> 00:59:44,720
The one who hurt my sister was

2059
00:59:44,720 --> 00:59:45,600
Manager Tui.

2060
00:59:45,600 --> 00:59:48,540
(Liu Lian Wangfan's sister
is also one of the victims)

2061
00:59:48,840 --> 00:59:50,480
How was your sister hurt?

2062
00:59:51,400 --> 00:59:53,280
That day, I was browsing a website

2063
00:59:53,280 --> 00:59:55,160
when a pop-up suddenly appeared.

2064
00:59:55,160 --> 00:59:57,520
The pop-up showed a minor

2065
00:59:57,520 --> 00:59:59,000
in a swimsuit advertisement.

2066
00:59:59,280 --> 01:00:00,120
Then I realized the face

2067
01:00:00,120 --> 01:00:01,560
actually belonged to my sister, Lei.

2068
01:00:01,560 --> 01:00:02,560
Lei?

2069
01:00:02,560 --> 01:00:04,200
That little girl of yours.

2070
01:00:04,200 --> 01:00:04,880
My student.

2071
01:00:04,880 --> 01:00:06,440
(Lei is Liu Lian Wangfan's sister)
The one playing piano is Lei.

2072
01:00:07,280 --> 01:00:08,880
The manager was having them

2073
01:00:08,880 --> 01:00:11,520
pose in front of a mirror,

2074
01:00:11,520 --> 01:00:13,080
mimicking adult poses.

2075
01:00:13,080 --> 01:00:14,720
I asked Lei what was going on.

2076
01:00:14,720 --> 01:00:16,160
She said a few days ago,

2077
01:00:16,160 --> 01:00:18,080
when she was at Starlight Cafe,

2078
01:00:18,080 --> 01:00:19,240
she ran into Manager Tui.

2079
01:00:19,240 --> 01:00:21,200
He told her she was pretty

2080
01:00:21,480 --> 01:00:23,920
and took her to
a mirror to practice smiling.

2081
01:00:23,920 --> 01:00:25,320
I suspected that mirror

2082
01:00:25,320 --> 01:00:26,960
was used for hidden filming.

2083
01:00:26,960 --> 01:00:28,500
(Manager Tui was capturing
faces from behind the mirror)

2084
01:00:28,720 --> 01:00:30,680
So I went to confront Manager Tui.

2085
01:00:30,680 --> 01:00:31,520
However, he didn't

2086
01:00:31,520 --> 01:00:32,600
even care.

2087
01:00:32,600 --> 01:00:34,760
Then her teachers,

2088
01:00:34,760 --> 01:00:35,480
classmates,

2089
01:00:35,480 --> 01:00:37,320
and parents all found out.

2090
01:00:37,320 --> 01:00:38,920
She came to me in tears and said,

2091
01:00:38,920 --> 01:00:39,880
"Brother,"

2092
01:00:39,880 --> 01:00:41,760
"I can't protect myself."

2093
01:00:41,820 --> 01:00:42,820
(She did nothing wrong)

2094
01:00:42,820 --> 01:00:44,780
(Yet she couldn't clear her name thanks
to a convincing AI-generated video)

2095
01:00:44,800 --> 01:00:46,720
I just couldn't take it anymore.

2096
01:00:46,720 --> 01:00:47,760
If I can't be there

2097
01:00:47,760 --> 01:00:49,680
to protect you every second,

2098
01:00:50,000 --> 01:00:51,640
then I'll take out

2099
01:00:51,640 --> 01:00:53,120
the monster who hurt you!

2100
01:00:53,120 --> 01:00:54,240
I was going to kill him!

2101
01:00:54,240 --> 01:00:56,500
(Liu Lian Wangfan's motive: to
protect his sister from further harm)

2102
01:00:58,280 --> 01:00:59,400
How?

2103
01:00:59,400 --> 01:00:59,520
Ya.

2104
01:00:59,520 --> 01:01:00,200
How were you going to do it?

2105
01:01:00,200 --> 01:01:00,720
With what?

2106
01:01:01,200 --> 01:01:02,440
(Admits to using a hammer)
A hammer.

2107
01:01:02,480 --> 01:01:04,120
So when this guy here

2108
01:01:05,120 --> 01:01:07,160
ironed your clothes for you,

2109
01:01:07,160 --> 01:01:07,920
did you steal them

2110
01:01:07,920 --> 01:01:09,480
to sneak

2111
01:01:09,480 --> 01:01:10,000
into the party?

2112
01:01:10,240 --> 01:01:11,520
Yes, I stole the outfit.

2113
01:01:11,520 --> 01:01:12,080
(Admits to stealing the puppet suit)

2114
01:01:12,080 --> 01:01:13,760
I had him iron it for me,

2115
01:01:13,760 --> 01:01:15,320
but he said he'd ruined it.

2116
01:01:15,320 --> 01:01:16,520
I was running out of time,

2117
01:01:16,520 --> 01:01:18,400
so I just put it on anyway.

2118
01:01:19,200 --> 01:01:20,760
Where did you get that ClearSight?

2119
01:01:20,760 --> 01:01:21,920
I found the bottle

2120
01:01:21,920 --> 01:01:23,560
when I arrived at the party.

2121
01:01:23,560 --> 01:01:25,240
(ClearSight bottle was found)
You found it at the party?

2122
01:01:25,240 --> 01:01:26,160
Yeah, I found it.

2123
01:01:26,160 --> 01:01:27,400
That night I'd been drinking.

2124
01:01:27,640 --> 01:01:28,800
Was it

2125
01:01:29,520 --> 01:01:31,360
the Starlight Special?

2126
01:01:31,360 --> 01:01:33,140
(Had the "special" drink)
The Starlight Special, yes.

2127
01:01:33,160 --> 01:01:33,720
That checks out.

2128
01:01:34,360 --> 01:01:35,920
If you found it, it was
already empty, right?

2129
01:01:36,840 --> 01:01:37,960
When I picked it up,

2130
01:01:37,960 --> 01:01:39,120
it was already empty.

2131
01:01:39,120 --> 01:01:40,480
(Medication was already used)
And I never touched the bottle.

2132
01:01:40,480 --> 01:01:41,960
So the pill had already been

2133
01:01:41,960 --> 01:01:42,920
taken by someone else.

2134
01:01:43,980 --> 01:01:45,780
(Capacity: one pill per bottle)

2135
01:01:48,720 --> 01:01:49,800
Someone already took it.

2136
01:01:49,800 --> 01:01:50,940
(The antidote was taken
by another suspect)

2137
01:01:51,360 --> 01:01:53,760
What time did you arrive

2138
01:01:53,760 --> 01:01:54,560
at Starlight Cafe today?

2139
01:01:57,760 --> 01:01:59,160
Around 6AM.

2140
01:01:59,260 --> 01:02:00,480
(Liu Lian Wangfan's timeline)

2141
01:02:00,480 --> 01:02:02,520
I put on the stolen puppet suit

2142
01:02:02,520 --> 01:02:04,640
(06:00 Entered cafe's VIP room)
and hit the backup button.

2143
01:02:04,640 --> 01:02:06,960
Manager Tui was doing push-ups.

2144
01:02:07,240 --> 01:02:08,560
(The boss in green was doing push-ups)
Standing or lying down?

2145
01:02:08,560 --> 01:02:09,320
Lying down.

2146
01:02:10,000 --> 01:02:10,760
I went up

2147
01:02:10,760 --> 01:02:12,080
and hit him with the hammer.

2148
01:02:12,080 --> 01:02:13,880
(Struck the back of his head)
Did your hammer have a special marking?

2149
01:02:14,200 --> 01:02:14,880
It's round.

2150
01:02:14,900 --> 01:02:16,500
(Liu Lian Wangfan's hammer was round)

2151
01:02:17,200 --> 01:02:17,800
He hit me.

2152
01:02:17,800 --> 01:02:18,160
Right.

2153
01:02:18,160 --> 01:02:18,820
(Liu Lian Wangfan attacked Qian Jinding)

2154
01:02:19,060 --> 01:02:20,350
(Qian Jinding's bandaged wound)
Mine was round.

2155
01:02:20,400 --> 01:02:22,680
Then she and I got into a fight.

2156
01:02:22,810 --> 01:02:24,040
(They fought)
She passed out.

2157
01:02:24,280 --> 01:02:25,920
Then everything went
black and I passed out too.

2158
01:02:26,120 --> 01:02:27,080
(Liu Lian Wangfan passed out)
Exact same thing.

2159
01:02:27,340 --> 01:02:28,790
(All suspects' accounts are consistent)
Same as ours.

2160
01:02:29,040 --> 01:02:30,560
I was doing push-ups

2161
01:02:30,560 --> 01:02:31,800
and got hit with a hammer.

2162
01:02:31,800 --> 01:02:32,760
(Qian Jinding, Liu Lian Wangfan)
Then we fought.

2163
01:02:33,080 --> 01:02:34,960
Everything went black and I passed out.

2164
01:02:34,960 --> 01:02:35,920
Then you went in.

2165
01:02:36,960 --> 01:02:38,720
(Ning Bubble)
I was pretending to do push-ups.

2166
01:02:38,920 --> 01:02:39,680
Then, "bam"!

2167
01:02:39,680 --> 01:02:41,000
I hit him.

2168
01:02:41,680 --> 01:02:42,120
Hearts.

2169
01:02:42,440 --> 01:02:43,160
Then we got into a scuffle.

2170
01:02:43,160 --> 01:02:43,840
(He Yiwei)
I grabbed his hair.

2171
01:02:43,840 --> 01:02:44,720
We were pulling each other's hair.

2172
01:02:44,720 --> 01:02:45,560
(Ke Coffee)
After a struggle,

2173
01:02:45,560 --> 01:02:46,240
everything went dark.

2174
01:02:46,240 --> 01:02:47,240
I blacked out.

2175
01:02:47,480 --> 01:02:49,320
All five have already come forward.

2176
01:02:49,320 --> 01:02:50,680
He's filled in

2177
01:02:50,680 --> 01:02:52,360
the missing piece for us.

2178
01:02:52,360 --> 01:02:52,960
Right.

2179
01:02:53,100 --> 01:02:55,010
(Actual flowchart of "five in, six out")

2180
01:02:55,020 --> 01:02:57,300
(In 2: Liu Lian Wangfan,
Out 3: Liu Lian Wangfan)

2181
01:02:57,320 --> 01:02:57,920
Alright.

2182
01:02:57,920 --> 01:02:58,960
That about covers it, right?

2183
01:02:59,320 --> 01:03:00,000
Pretty much.

2184
01:03:00,000 --> 01:03:01,520
Now it's time to beat them.

2185
01:03:01,520 --> 01:03:01,880
Right?

2186
01:03:03,400 --> 01:03:04,520
Those two guys aren't here yet.

2187
01:03:04,520 --> 01:03:05,400
They tried to scare us today.

2188
01:03:05,400 --> 01:03:06,720
Shouldn't we scare them back?

2189
01:03:06,720 --> 01:03:08,000
Let's show them what we've got.

2190
01:03:09,440 --> 01:03:10,360
Those two big guys...

2191
01:03:10,360 --> 01:03:11,420
(Just say it)

2192
01:03:11,560 --> 01:03:12,440
Easy.

2193
01:03:13,160 --> 01:03:14,760
We are the big guys, aren't we?

2194
01:03:15,080 --> 01:03:16,640
Those two will be here soon.

2195
01:03:16,640 --> 01:03:17,920
Will be here soon.

2196
01:03:17,920 --> 01:03:19,040
Forget it. Not worth it.

2197
01:03:19,040 --> 01:03:20,120
(Be the bigger person)
Why keep the cycle of revenge going?

2198
01:03:23,120 --> 01:03:24,560
Alright, here's the thing.

2199
01:03:24,560 --> 01:03:26,160
This cafe has already

2200
01:03:26,160 --> 01:03:27,600
shut your operation down.

2201
01:03:27,600 --> 01:03:29,520
I suggest you find another line of work.

2202
01:03:29,520 --> 01:03:30,840
There's a show on WeTV,

2203
01:03:30,840 --> 01:03:31,880
"Amazing Night".

2204
01:03:31,880 --> 01:03:33,600
Go sign up for Season 3.

2205
01:03:33,600 --> 01:03:34,560
(Detectives offering career advice)
Okay.

2206
01:03:34,800 --> 01:03:36,320
Maybe you'll have a shot.

2207
