2758
01:19:24,000 --> 01:19:24,280
So

2759
01:19:24,280 --> 01:19:25,680
I was really nervous toward the end.

2760
01:19:25,920 --> 01:19:27,000
No. I couldn't tell at all.

2761
01:19:27,000 --> 01:19:27,560
To be honest.

2762
01:19:27,880 --> 01:19:28,600
I was really nervous.

2763
