2802
01:20:26,240 --> 01:20:29,660
(Wang Yuwen x1
Jin Jing & Zhou Keyu & Sun Qian x0)

2803
01:20:32,000 --> 01:20:32,560
No.

2804
01:20:32,560 --> 01:20:34,440
