2811
01:20:43,880 --> 01:20:44,900
(I've "spoken")

2812
01:20:45,920 --> 01:20:46,440
I've "spoken".

2813
01:20:46,720 --> 01:20:47,800
Your highlight moment today

2814
01:20:47,800 --> 01:20:49,240
