2858
01:22:00,600 --> 01:22:01,320
Instinct.

2859
01:22:01,320 --> 01:22:01,680
Yes.

2860
01:22:02,480 --> 01:22:03,280
But she didn't pick me.

2861
01:22:03,640 --> 01:22:04,560
