2914
01:23:25,400 --> 01:23:27,080
(Mystery 2: Who was Tui Haomei referring to by "you all"?)
What do the people behind him...

2915
01:23:27,480 --> 01:23:28,200
I never imagined

2916
01:23:28,200 --> 01:23:29,480
