2918
01:23:31,320 --> 01:23:32,720
Who exactly is Mr. Tui?

2919
01:23:32,720 --> 01:23:33,440
Mr. Tui.

2920
01:23:33,440 --> 01:23:34,400
Who is he?

2921
01:23:34,400 --> 01:23:36,440
Luckily, I met a man

2922
01:23:36,440 --> 01:23:38,000
surnamed Tui.

2923
01:23:38,000 --> 01:23:39,280
What a coincidence.

2924
01:23:39,280 --> 01:23:41,920
The two Tuis will team up
and make a fortune together.

2925
01:23:41,920 --> 01:23:45,520
Mr. Tui provided me
with technical support.

2926
01:23:45,620 --> 01:23:46,180
(The case's mysteries)

2927
01:23:46,180 --> 01:23:46,870
(1. Is Tui Haomei dead?)

2928
01:23:46,870 --> 01:23:47,680
(2. Besides Manager Tui, who was)

2929
01:23:47,680 --> 01:23:48,640
