What do they want?)

2930
01:23:48,640 --> 01:23:49,200
(3; Who is Mr. Tui?)

2931
01:23:49,200 --> 01:23:49,740
(4. What is tuiwangwang?)

2932
01:23:49,760 --> 01:23:51,280
So we'll keep investigating

2933
01:23:51,280 --> 01:23:52,520
tomorrow.

2934
01:23:52,520 --> 01:23:53,360
Yes.

2935
01:23:53,360 --> 01:23:54,360
At the same time,

2936
01:23:54,360 --> 01:23:55,480
we'll also have

2937
01:23:55,480 --> 01:23:56,600
