2967
01:24:32,240 --> 01:24:33,680
(Another identity as a VIP guest)
You all work here,

2968
01:24:33,680 --> 01:24:34,120
but I...

2969
01:24:34,640 --> 01:24:35,680
No.

2970
01:24:35,680 --> 01:24:36,440
You have to continue

2971
01:24:36,440 --> 01:24:38,320
to be our customer.

2972
01:24:38,320 --> 01:24:39,120
VIP.

2973
01:24:41,120 --> 01:24:42,440
Firstly, I want my money back

2974
01:24:42,440 --> 01:24:44,480
because my pride is all gone.

2975
01:24:44,480 --> 01:24:45,280
If you really

2976
01:24:45,280 --> 01:24:46,480
need anything,

2977
01:24:46,960 --> 01:24:48,280
your membership is still...

2978
01:24:48,840 --> 01:24:49,160
Right.

2979
01:24:49,160 --> 01:24:49,440
Okay.

2980
01:24:52,840 --> 01:24:53,440
I can use it?

2981
01:24:53,440 --> 01:24:54,960
You're still a Gold Card member.

2982
01:24:55,680 --> 01:24:56,240
You can still

2983
01:24:56,240 --> 01:24:57,680
