2986
01:25:03,840 --> 01:25:04,160
Hang on.

2987
01:25:05,260 --> 01:25:06,460
(Source of the sound)

2988
01:25:06,480 --> 01:25:07,800
Is there something more?

2989
01:25:11,320 --> 01:25:12,600
When will this end?

2990
01:25:14,660 --> 01:25:16,220
