3000
01:25:41,040 --> 01:25:41,680
Hello.

3001
01:25:42,720 --> 01:25:43,960
Don't worry, just keep moving forward.

3002
01:25:43,960 --> 01:25:45,000
I'm right in front of you guys.

3003
01:25:46,100 --> 01:25:47,100
(Inching forward)

3004
01:25:47,120 --> 01:25:48,080
It's okay.

3005
01:25:48,080 --> 01:25:49,080
It's fine.

3006
01:25:50,200 --> 01:25:50,960
Just...

3007
01:25:50,960 --> 01:25:51,720
