3028
01:26:14,720 --> 01:26:15,640
Tui Haomei, is that you?

3029
01:26:17,040 --> 01:26:18,400
Are you Tui Haomei?

3030
01:26:18,400 --> 01:26:19,680
I'm Ke Coffee.

3031
01:26:21,600 --> 01:26:22,200
Ke.

3032
01:26:22,200 --> 01:26:22,760
It's me.

3033
01:26:22,760 --> 01:26:23,240
Is that you?

3034
01:26:23,240 --> 01:26:23,760
